MERCURIES LIFE said unconsolidated sales
in February fell 8.90% to NT$9,101,645,000 from NT$9,990,327,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  2/2011           2/2010
Sales           9,101,645        9,990,327   
YOY%              -8.90%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales           20,492,210       26,051,570  
YOY%             -21.34% 
=================================================================
 